  "html_size": 181945,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220540023773\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220540023773\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>바쁜 토요일</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>자주 오시는 환자분께서 아드님이랑 치료받으러&nbsp;내원하셨다</p><p><br /></p><p>들어오셔서 데스크로 오시더니</p><p>\"이건 아메리카노 이건 라떼\"하시면서 건네주셨다</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3fc2ad90ebe085a6.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:360px;\" id=\"20151115_161/isuhani_14475888812934fcnF_JPEG/PB144925.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000335935B3DD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3fc2ad90ebe085a6.jpg\"><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><br style=\"clear:both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/590c14607e9935b2.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:480px; rheight:360px;\" id=\"20151115_122/isuhani_1447588881922XViq5_JPEG/PB144927.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000335935B3DD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/590c14607e9935b2.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p>그리고 점심시간 쯤 되서는 다른 환자분께서는...&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">요걸 갖다주셨어요...</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br /></span></p><p>짠~</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fa6eb4025706df2f.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:360px;\" id=\"20151115_217/isuhani_1447589823962E0IcX_JPEG/PB144934.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000335935B3DD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fa6eb4025706df2f.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>KFC 햄버거랑 감자튀김이랑 음료수</p><p>점심시간이라고 열심히 일하는 저희를 위해 사주셨습니다</p><p><br /></p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fa78c6dc40535c86.png\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-15\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p>오후에는 예전에 계셨던 실장님이 치료받으러 오셨는데,&nbsp;</p><p>오시는길에 빈손으로 오기 그렇다고 구지 빵집에 들리셔서 사오셨데요 ㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8fa10982731c5d5f.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"487\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:480px; rheight:487px;\" id=\"20151115_139/isuhani_1447590503044hr37I_JPEG/PB144936.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000335935B3DD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8fa10982731c5d5f.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151115_107/isuhani_1447590544704lYuRe_JPEG/PB144930.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"319\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth:480px; rheight:319px;\" id=\"20151115_107/isuhani_1447590544704lYuRe_JPEG/PB144930.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000335935B3DD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20151115_107/isuhani_1447590544704lYuRe_JPEG/PB144930.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p>모두 감사합니다</p><p>잘먹었습니다</p><p>커피도 햄버거도 쿠키도 ^^</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7e27ce44253d1090.png\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-31\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
